      <title>Windows Authenticode 签名验证变更将于6月通过自动更新启用</title>
      <link>https://qife122.github.io/p/windows-authenticode-%E7%AD%BE%E5%90%8D%E9%AA%8C%E8%AF%81%E5%8F%98%E6%9B%B4%E5%B0%86%E4%BA%8E6%E6%9C%88%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87%E8%87%AA%E5%8A%A8%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0%E5%90%AF%E7%94%A8/</link>
